#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; is a simple one player strategy game played against the "
#| "computer. The playing field is an 8 by 8 square board divided into 64 "
#| "squares. The game pieces used are two sided stones, where each side has "
#| "its own, distinctive color. If a piece is captured by an opposing player, "
#| "that piece is turned over to reveal the color of that player. A winner is "
#| "declared when one player has more pieces of his own color on the board "
#| "and there are no more possible moves."
msgid ""
"&kreversi; is a simple one player strategy game played against the computer. "
"The playing field is an 8 by 8 square board divided into 64 squares. The "
"game pieces used are two sided stones, where each side has its own, "
"distinctive color. If a piece is captured by an opposing player, that piece "
"is turned over to reveal the color of that player. A winner is declared when "
"one player has more pieces of his own color on the board and there are no "
"more possible moves."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; je jednostavna strateška igra koju igrač igra protiv računara.  "
"Polje igre je 8x8 kvadratna ploča podijeljena na 64 kvadrata. Igra se igra "
"sa dvostranim žetonima, gdje svaka strana ima svoju, karakterističnu boju.  "
"Ako je žeton zarobljen od strane suprotnog igrača, taj se žeton okreče na "
"boju tog igrača.  Pobjednik je igrač koji ima više žetona svoje boje na "
"ploči kada nema više mogućih poteza."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Get control over the majority of squares on the board."
msgstr "Uspostavite kontrolu nad većinom polja na ploči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; loads directly into the game play mode. As a first player you "
#| "have the right to move first."
msgid ""
"&kreversi; loads directly into the <guilabel>New game</guilabel> dialog "
"where you select the game mode, &ie; play against the computer or another "
"human player. As a first player you have the right to move first."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; direktno učitava mod igranja. Kao prvi igrač imate pravo prvog "
"poteza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default the human player always has a right to the first move."
msgstr "Prema zadanim postavkama čovjek uvijek ima pravo prvog poteza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, imagine yourself that with each move your stone has to hop (jump) over "
"the enemy's one (or ones, as there might be more than one stone). Yet, your "
"stone does not relocate after the move, instead a new stone is placed on the "
"board onto where your stone would have appeared if it indeed could jump. "
"Once the move is done, all the enemy stones that you jump over, become yours "
"and change their color respectively."
msgstr ""
"Sada, zamislite kako pri svakom potezu Vaš žeton treba da skoči preko jednog "
"protivničkog(ili više njih, obzirom da može biti više od jednog žetona).  "
"Ipak, Vaš žeton ne mijenja lokaciju nakon poteza,  već se postavlja novi "
"žeton na ploču tamo gdje bi Vaš bio postavljen kada bi zaista mogao skočiti. "
"Jednom kada je potez završen,  svi protivnički žetoni, koje je Vaš žeton "
"preskočio, postaju Vaši i mijenjaju boju jedan po jedan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Every single move you do in &kappname; has to be done in this manner. And "
#| "you can jump your stones vertically, horizontally and diagonally. But, in "
#| "case there is nowhere to jump, your turn will automatically skip."
msgid ""
"Every single move you do in &kreversi; has to be done in this manner. And "
"you can jump your stones vertically, horizontally and diagonally. But, in "
"case there is nowhere to jump, your turn will automatically skip."
msgstr ""
"Svaki potez koji napravite u &kappname; mora biti napravljen na ovaj način. "
"Možete skakati sa žetonima vertikalno, horizontalno i dijagonalno. Ali, u "
"slućaju da nemate gdje skočiti, Vaš potez će biti automatski preskočen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same rule applies to your enemy. If there is no possibility to make a "
"move the turn is skipped."
msgstr ""
"Ista pravila vrijede i za protivnika. Ukoliko nema mogućnosti da se napravi "
"korak, potez se preskače."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea here is to fill the board with the stones of your own color. The "
"player who manages to conquer the most of the game board is announced the "
"winner."
msgstr ""
"Ideja je da popuniti ploču žetonima Vaše boje. Igrač koji uspije osvojiti "
"većinu ploče će pobijediti."

